May-sAUBLzy2yLtZvI8uqA2Y6KWh8V3u2AZ0nQbeTSKSaw/wBhloj4J0vf0RqXIboJUx5fV2FD3PVDF/9" target="_blank"&gt;威胁到美国的动摇政府制度&lt;/a&gt;。针对特朗普的抗议活动在全国各地蔓延，整个周末都有计划。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/m7uCSeBVMDzUVbjiixH0wO9p3eDJsipi60eiZH69fWmvOCeeGiuAOmL41f99ME9AoDR_Vu2p1VbLbYCxKkvy3C-7JWqMa7XgV5iliTlPFd3PFc4uyCNd4PI9osiMVKgh-tnndv4ePilMNUvR0kgheQooDj7UnZRQZ0zOuaqKna4HvNYIHLqXklvxXqSk01Y6rURZilzTPGQ_7DLPjI644ysw7pd5uJxfvpRoutzhQ-W7Loz8kRHY1VvbV_c63mxcADkZmgVU7ZRcs5-gslauYGiOMGkovGwWVQ9Y2I8vj4behfoPzapB6oGXWuIbLU6z026w3eKsxOoE-N7AzpRgeKK0DDNrY0rrCHIekm3XF3o/BEdvOwBBRovkBzaaI632VOzYlzfSiF0A/9" target="_blank"&gt;特朗普&lt;/a&gt;毫不犹豫地赦免了他的数百名追随者在2021年1月6日致命的袭击美国国会大厦的袭击中， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/gwNZmvbvxvk6bDfBkZbeBvdltZdExluCSxKipFNkA128Z084QjfqaCLce5SgWxuK9ifWOqoQq75Hns66rCn8_vZmQp6FO4S9jWMFJNuBZrz3a6QY9sssmbGJ0t_8er3Qenrg72_IDSYZZkzuqFtrlaVNSz9BtVSY1zJw5JwnmTPxEOiow4dhM7KufiaJt4hk_b90laYbauNJxUyJcnE8b2DVUyMHH8esMwzQVFxxaL2cKzDBzvSy_JLS82Ma4gdOpdQEGcpp_9IuD5iiNvCM4AicWp5T-9r7XFlRB61dI67ST_CDvYOeM-9U5_8TFjZAfsIx0_BX2GOXgYnmSCEOpU89b8gOWF2BVfTibMFKcr-vEkNb7ZhE54dXGQkKlvG_WRL4/uCYaQRNsPKOIlojcgckHnGQJE6_rwbZ9/9" target="_blank"&gt;对美国人的暴力威胁造成了薄薄的威胁，&lt;/a&gt;他们对美国人抗议他在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1tRKTl7937sKFl7Mqibqo6kKY1Z9Kz16-nxSoPwuKgPsnd0pu2ZCYw8etRttU0a5UHdpRPaLN8Dk4y4yzTlf-ekhZQ1BrbxuNffH4p50JUa9BOl71La7_JWxvX25y2xr_XFdSl8hOcRkT6pWfEP9UcuY6oOcFaexvZM6YQspOlOgRz2xyAHnIfoTXK_duQEMfD4aZ5Pvb5xRO5BYyt-c-Bo7YNYdRgOpLMkYxB-MTd1VZNp7AKkGex68OBZZ88PieqtrJi1T5DT2OP-lGSEX1NcfH-IoJ5ZLYdzW-0ZMyKvfqTVXx0cBBWFQP3K_46TTXFX5Wz3iGG8N1A4QUyICjs3p8cY1uOpaibdsUH7GriDu0n7bfVniDd8x1R1M4B8pDKDVP-M/p7LWZJyIdC7We6eGeGOZPrw5RbUhSLWy/9" target="_blank"&gt;华盛顿&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/VclchIeiL4fw6QyyxCYm1D2zsgWD_SA-oObpg-KYLCTe1J2qrThEj4BHo6OzFOoWUjTFzVJby2y84V6mLwnpo5NJ_lyGcELvpKVPi6oAzsERK8WYxVLIIKg1bmxUHdWP20Dys7WheHpqScKVTEbr_O