ily: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;交易最新。&lt;/strong&gt;美国和中国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AVPxXjr2suz-qGagX6veLCwpTiTzX9tAUAFWpwJf1G3KRNebWP64pnVhO-dFTH726AL9xw86Ea4Vu7xPMfuyxA7iYb3T1WXuXbIzMMrOjUBNTmnoIo47Z64SfL6dRhNUJqfqnfjQsTUqi1XGqxapOgsu9qZ7gQzxSn4TtSjoXHin8hTCAIlExonN1jH6LRsPTP4KmANmCxospw1XA0I-InTJR2yveMhM4pWk1NMCZCMvP_eOCnm4gAB4hCqBB6MKk4OnsECsd7JvkKF1wGz5ZOpzMQ/rGDQDsGvi4EouQQI291FTE1Z1F6FOVUt/9" target="_blank"&gt;同意了恢复敏感商品流动的计划的概述&lt;/a&gt;。美国商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）表示，北京承诺加快&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/3jRFUpLA94XOUo7ctMwUsVqm8KNi8VpdjsiXJyaA75BXeOUHi9bwqpiHbmlfUMsjm4I7Kn2apT8EbIyZ_ivvekb61tFd8lpLIG980ItnL6DQTJntJSjtEV8LQt-cPIgcmVcHhsr4iSPnXhvvJLV7E5ION6rNZamhKYPUpvbyVEsUIlNHW-IzygLR2FwZUmLllnCIMvYAe-wXBcFuIsVJPLB4_37ZdBskYHmBAvM950-RbWBkvFJfSMha98y36cS-US_jqcKh05c8qq_P4hPG_c9awg/37Fs7TDsG7tdTMLzwxcAQgwLkzE7file/9" target="_blank"&gt;稀土金属货物的&lt;/a&gt;加快，而华盛顿将缓解一些出口控制。该协议仍然需要唐纳德·特朗普和习近平的批准。随着这一过程的发展，上诉法院裁定特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/1J_26-wHCGwQF7Ffk0V0guwTs2_22Zpc3-7Owdh9xiS32F5lR-l4yIUjYv2Ll5U7pBDxoq2YbuOU6z7hTN0PKkSw-1bP4MIcd0fzuE8mklNnJ7KNZExLLN6afOUY4Cp2dMJ4sI3kFY_EbIM1V95rfhyqpfrWLLXi5S8qi7wrMQKQ76SnB1ZZdN2-TrLIGp3sp0GJ7SDY4Ez3ptN1aK9wTCpREeQVchRtGC9-IV3Bwmo5etf7JPTu4T9oAYeVGo9F-Gegvr8f2CgoU1NMkKM2Ki7Hjw/DlLpufHV8tKPZTbJhGIUaup3dwoUImnd/9" target="_blank"&gt;目前可以将其全球关税保持在适当的位置&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;交易中&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;缺乏细节&lt;/strong&gt;并没有给&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7hiL3di7ckqeszxYYVK7zgg_u5myU0kmqgSLW_wJPh-pPwvf6UYac7umoLceUtSkh9jDwR7T2GRplA2VB8RZ4qbAaWU0-plfxmiL06wPGNTtcOZYP590PsCOjCQVueivRpzGvKvkWyNr3p5mbzbtTkX3W4OzMXIqy0UN1DdBHGFNZlMvC_9UzlvyMYzjiT8In664tZORfE8ruG-pyoTPt1SY-NdUfDM0jqn17Ao18MKb2qSQoyVQ6fIWHDQF7q1iucY_yT5Z4-b82yt7Ea4MCVYF_g/Jwdpa1wSn0RyGN7rm47qgcRUIHEZ9skv/9" target="_blank"&gt;美国股票期货蘸酱&lt;/a&gt;留下深刻的印象。由于预测者预计，关税的影响可能会在6月更明显，但注意力预期的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/yq0KF0efiQGL8dScsKL-Xff0LoyjIBxgQap1JT-mkNm_MnTTxIKqMDX0QSNYW8wecu2U2kiekDKf9YuVbLBHLnBtREDGe-KL6WIXl9A0kdF1mCNU8G0K170bSJExZtpwc-lOiyT6kP3dFeoadj-QcCYO7uYZCbXh-v3GnTR97czqAnEISJrdeo7xt_r8TT-NCdPQD_-WqEeugFMyB4-FD3L17C9d4enqnzQZpSEb9daEo0lKqyrA9rNUi77yS6Yral1qbiKlru2f_0p-ZXz3_Jxqyw/_rhZuQbTW_SU_5ij_d_rDkSInybkQXuV/9" target="_blank"&gt;消费者&lt;/a&gt;价格可能会更加明显。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/VgRbDnxjsuteo7ZUIsQR0uYYZ8nR3gZ2BObnKssucmadWIqE0Fpe7uQUcTiQu0PsaPAI_3Gdrp-gPM6SAABjMOns0M4thM68iLyBpTHRS0Z7XhMOoqX1X1oLeQ_RO8ZdXKSOmmTsWWT_5Hwaln7tn7UDhLwp3cGEKIbWkhqPiiVIL8KACUYrluuj4hRZzkrYc2zCV_QbuNywMIV3BMH-jxkWSggytN0JxUt6I41FoDePjLS4RVPoagkG_SoOnkx4nZ44NPZt8dnENK93kYNq4NquGw/vxqrEO3NE3xDixfwBfjLQrGFF8vbU_1b/9" target="_blank"&gt;在此处保持主要市场主题&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;洛杉矶&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/8A6jaHaGlbcsTYb1mB41SkH6GAQaf9f2vlLTUPZHW0ZPhzSbygRIhRiyOJhpRgEvrKkMOHXSHVvitvH7V9qUuU9bAhlrHk8FJiU4XRP50z-_hXYRr6SwTorJ_wkj49Xyg-JLJvdByfGetNtovuhKk7L_OLN3J7xcwtN4Do6ntRa_rzGvugv-YpLVAEUOfxEwaxPqI7QV5BeLfgxJ6z4HsHryfQQO2QkBOKIVWXuRTQWPhEPkxVyKPVd-lHDzi1TZuAe1v26q2HqXUwFtaQvno775Xw/xsElOaIggtkRY0Zh7c-smxdrQtkU5OJw/9" target="_blank"&gt;为市中心的一部分制定了宵禁&lt;/a&gt;，导致了一个安静的夜晚，而反冰抗议活动则蔓延到其他城市，包括芝加哥，纽约和亚特兰大。这是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/JOoyO7wZ5UtOpO414iazpuFOxW8TgxmvFfPcm0mGrK7XY8C_vqb-VBSAdTXsjeCKyH9rnZyuqMgnVQS3W17V00ZoNOi8NdtafDE5pqJX0TI7hhL1pO1zvqaztCMMuTLf9nzTG2WnJp897UaDnMUsUJ2JRDRokKl6b3IuDIeX9P4ZaiuMvC3nX-rfAaBnYTZBxUYhIYgElQ8dqsQYNGEZKTUxfX7It_N_KmXnOkQew9dR6WVLS6MTGwU9_qYpIGxrzdxFno9irQaimouokaHoPgjMow/isVPEzW3eh93MpsKczibZ53G7hFe10FH/9" target="_blank"&gt;关于为什么特朗普决定在抗议活动中将军事部署到洛杉矶的解释&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/